cleanDesc: Lamin-X Clear Bra Front Protection Kit - E46 M3
short-description: BMW M3 (01-06) Lamin-x Clear Bra paint protection protects your paint finish from stone chips, scrapes, bugs, and other paint damaging items with an invisible protective layer. Quite possibly the best investment you will make toward protecting your vehicle.The clear bra is a strong and invisible poly-urethane protective film that applies directly onto the surface of your vehicle. This kit is custom pre-cut to fit and protect the leading areas of your hood, fenders, mirrors, and entire front bumper from all normal wear and tear. Our paint protection films are manufactured by the industry's leading paint protection manufacturers right here in the USA. This allows us to give you reassurance by providing you with a 5 year product warranty.
